How To Create AWS EC2 Instance With Terraform

1. Get AMI ID need to create 

2. Write terraform main.tf and provider.tf
  
3.Run cerate EC2 instance with terraform
 
commands:
        > terraform init : now terraform wiil be initialized
        > now see the hidden files you will find a terraform directory
        > terrafprm plan : Read config fike and compare local state file
 	> terraform apply : now terraform.tf state file will be created which consists of all the metadata
        > terraform destroy : Kill the instance
       
